#Advertising - but from the heart.
Especially the thoughtful ones are the ones who do not submit to the spirit of the times and thus become lateral thinkers.
By avoiding the superficialities of social life and the custom of adaptation that is widespread there, they increasingly fall into solitude, because those who swim against the tide , swim alone.
Love for loneliness arises only as a result of experience, reflection, development and search.
It is about deliberately withdrawing from the hustle and bustle of everyday life - at least temporarily - to gather ones wits, in order to find peace of mind.
The loneliness, this loneliness leads into abundance !
